{"tid":556823,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人既人生都想係咁？","createTime":"2018-02-10T18:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T03:45:29.000Z","uid":158541,"like":54,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3ca47a32ce71f03f7fb023072c3e2cf0689fafa2","tid":556823,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T18:57:48.000Z","msg":"男又好 女又好 你地有冇諗過將來完全唔想結婚 搵到一個可以佢面前展現到真正自己既知己就算 <br />\n而加打工賺錢只係想自己一個去旅行 去見識下呢個世界 例如睇下唔同既古蹟 文化 <br />\n盡量去享受自己認為人生 唔想被呢個社會去束縛住自己  <br />\n<br />\n雖然屋企家境唔太好 又有個唔係好好既阿爸 但係好好彩搵到幾個知己 先令到我既人生冇咁太壓力 我真係願意用三百響頭去多謝佢地<br />\n<br />\n利申：想係三十歲前 去到世界一半既地方"},{"pid":"255f5aa0a5654230f2938ca8a8ee9fd86b3590a3","tid":556823,"uid":62167,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:02:43.000Z","msg":"本來無一物，何處惹塵埃"},{"pid":"b1b8eb9fd8fcd1aacf28d9a6c1e7ae71b85993f0","tid":556823,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本來無一物，何處惹塵埃</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f87a80f0eff0be15e42cbcee77930660f68eb5","tid":556823,"uid":151872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:27:20.000Z","msg":"樓主宜家幾歲"},{"pid":"991ccfbaea90989994cb179844385c99a52ec7bf","tid":556823,"uid":47147,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:28:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ffb280230f5e00518db3be4526dd91eff59afd21","tid":556823,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主宜家幾歲</blockquote><br />\n19"},{"pid":"e14b5d8f724c447a6a4e880f7ed74e9c5b48a142","tid":556823,"uid":2861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ffb280230f5e00518db3be4526dd91eff59afd21","tid":556823,"uid":158541,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主宜家幾歲</blockquote><br />\n19"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-10T19:33:57.000Z","msg":"